<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 30 at 9:08AM CST  by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>...Areas of freezing fog this morning...
Patchy areas of freezing fog have developed across portions of the
northeastern combined Panhandles this morning. Visibility will be
down to a quarter mile at times and will linger for the next hour
or two before conditions improve across the region. Please use
caution while driving this morning as the fog may be freezing to
roadways.</description>
